Cursor
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fBDESCRIPTION\fR
.sp 2
Return result set in the type of array.
.SH "Examples"
\fBExamples\fR
.sp 2
Select records with the value of "age" greater than 5 in the
collection "bar" and return the amount of record in the range
from current cursor to final cursor.
.sp 2
db.foo.bar.find({age:{$gt:10}}).size()
.sp 2
Return:{
